    • build

      @NotNull public @NotNull ProcessorServer build​(@Nullable @Nullable io.grpc.ServerBuilder<?> serverBuilder)
      Deprecated.
      Builds a processor server that can be used to host the processor using a grpc server builder. The port specified by ProcessorServer.Builder.getPort() will not be used and instead the one already configured on the serverBuilder parameter will be used.
      Parameters:
      serverBuilder - The grpc server builder.
      Returns:
      Processor server object.
